{"tid":683643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防竊取技術 美擬縮短中國研究生居留簽証僅能停留1年","createTime":"2018-05-30T01:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T01:44:17.000Z","uid":35790,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1f001f11f20793b193e15aed2184e964517b1fa5","tid":683643,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:11:07.000Z","msg":"防竊取技術 美擬縮短中國研究生居留簽証<br />\n<br />\n美國為了防範中國竊取高科技機密，打算限制部分中國公民赴美簽證期限。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報導，美國國務院計畫自6月11日起，對中國部分研究生核發的赴美簽證將限制僅能停留1年。匿名官員透露，簽證居留期受限的研究生主要為研究機械、航空及高科技產<br />\n<br />\n業類別。這些研究領域被中國列為「中國製造2025」計畫重點。<br />\n<br />\n此外，如果中國公民在屬於美國商務部特別審查名單中的機構及企業擔任研究員或經理，<br />\n<br />\n他們需要獲得多個美國機構的特別許可才能申請簽證，預料過程將長達數月。<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/FAoaSf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFAoaSf&d=YPZKdr1hWSu%2FId2ZQmbT9JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=efc8f009\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/FAoaSf</a>"},{"pid":"c480dfd14e9f6ae2e7eb505f02e04f7779ffde19","tid":683643,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aba87359f0568f9fa93b28fff5042a87ef3b7c1","tid":683643,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:12:51.000Z","msg":"一年就要番中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83cfa1d398c52aca9107209fdbec7afeb1319e45","tid":683643,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:16:34.000Z","msg":"如果中國公民在屬於美國商務部特別審查名單中的機構及企業擔任研究員或經理，<br />\n他們需要獲得多個美國機構的特別許可才能申請簽證，預料過程將長達數月。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9904459ae715f433ce6be65faf53ecb71c1348fe","tid":683643,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T01:19:13.000Z","msg":"咁咪更多人去德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgm